Package ZetaFish.NetworkObjects

Class Summary
ZFCard An object of type Card represents a playing card from a standard Poker deck, including Jokers.
ZFCardRequest Represents a message to the server to ask an opponent for a card.
ZFCardRequestResponse The ZFCardRequestResponse is the partner to the ZFCardRequest.
ZFChat The ZFChat object is used to pass as chat message from players to the server which should broadcast it to all players.
ZFCommand Network object used to send command to the server.
ZFDeck An object of type Deck represents a deck of playing cards.
ZFPlayBook The ZFPlayBook object is used to allow a given player to play a book during his/her turn.
ZFPlayer ZFPlayer is used by other Network Object to represent a given player.
ZFRemovePlayer The ZFRemovePlayer is sent from the server to all clients to signal that a player has unexpectedly left the game.
ZFStatus The ZFStatus object will be passed to all clients whenever the game state changes.
 

Enum Summary
ZFCard.Suits  
ZFCardRequestResponse.CardRequestResult Determines if cards came from the player or were drawn from the ocean.
ZFCommand.CommandType Commands
ZFStatus.StatusType Status types
